{"tid":1867891,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"俄羅斯首批撤離僑民抵俄被送往西伯利亞 營區以圍牆及CCTV包圍 軍人駐守出入口","createTime":"2020-02-07T10:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T01:23:02.000Z","uid":133680,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5c47ab856846d9eb28d83004f06560b54b621d9c","tid":1867891,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:38:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6770573/article-%E6%90%AD%E8%BB%8D%E6%A9%9F%E6%92%A以圍牆包圍4%E9%9B%A2%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2-%E4%BF%84%E5%83%91%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%A8%E8%A5%BF%E4%BC%AF%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9E%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A22%E5%91%A8/?ismobile=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6770573%2Farticle-%25E6%2590%25AD%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%2592%25A%E4%BB%A5%E5%9C%8D%E7%89%86%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D4%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2-%25E4%25BF%2584%25E5%2583%2591%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%259C%25A8%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25BC%25AF%25E5%2588%25A9%25E4%25BA%259E%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A22%25E5%2591%25A8%2F%3Fismobile%3Dtrue&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=dceb65ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/6770573/article-%E6%90%AD%E8%BB%8D%E6%A9%9F%E6%92%A以圍牆包圍4%E9%9B%A2%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2-%E4%BF%84%E5%83%91%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%A8%E8%A5%BF%E4%BC%AF%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9E%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A22%E5%91%A8/?ismobile=true</a><br />\n<br />\n100多名俄羅斯人5日開始在西伯利亞一個營地進行為期兩個星期的隔離。此前他們被從新型冠狀病毒疫情中心武漢疏散。<br />\n<br />\n路透報導，俄羅斯已對來往於俄中邊界的人員實行限制。俄羅斯跟中國的邊界線長達4300公里。上個星期，俄羅斯報告查出兩例病毒感染病例，地點均在西伯利亞，而且都是中國公民。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音報導，在疏散回國的兩批144名俄羅斯公民中，沒有發現任何感染病例。俄羅斯國防部說，這些人星期三乘坐兩架軍機飛抵秋明機場。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯冠狀病毒危機應對中心提供的電視畫面顯示，身穿白色隔離服的醫護人員星期三上午迎接伊爾-76軍用運輸機疏散的第一批僑民的到來。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯衛生官員稱，所有被疏散的僑民將在秋明外大約30公里的一個營地接受兩個星期的隔離。據稱，這個營地有圍牆，配備閉路電視，有軍人巡邏把守。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯衛生部官員稱，俄羅斯正在為疫情可能蔓延做準備，一些學校停課，公共活動被取消。不過，也有其他官員稱這是在應對流感。<br />\n<br />\n目前，新冠病毒疫情在全球已經造成近500人死亡，報告確認感染病例近2萬5000例。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯官員估計有600多俄羅斯人在武漢所在的湖北省。路透報導，俄羅斯駐北京大使館發言人葉戈洛夫說，所有表示希望返回俄羅斯的人都已經返回，俄羅斯將不再安排接運僑民的飛機。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯先前已經中止來自中國的直達鐵路客車和商業航班。現在，莫斯科機場只是有一個單獨的航站可以准許來自中國的旅客入境，因為那裡比較方便對旅客進行篩查。"},{"pid":"8b171dd9fb28a961b2b3d0100b74a211a6dd6866","tid":1867891,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:40:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd99c67527dd5ae9ccc74ae6a74e3d6469e42204","tid":1867891,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:41:18.000Z","msg":"冬天的冠軍"},{"pid":"0e391b8e499a5fc820cf339044bafbd03b202d28","tid":1867891,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cea4cad2480d4bb00d244d97db1fe54db71d8b0","tid":1867891,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:49:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33efbbda6d4bed181a94e415b67bd3df62c61dbe","tid":1867891,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:18:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ee770bf17ce898acc3e3c1ddba2b3a6f741784","tid":1867891,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d828a13644f4057c4d203dd9ddd4f883fd43def7","tid":1867891,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:09:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d27e1e2f775b506126c05762fde07899bdf3495","tid":1867891,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159338affb25995babc6d755168a40da8d02ffe7","tid":1867891,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi